ndian_subcontinent" title="Indian subcontinent">Indian subcontinent</a></td>\n<td><a href="/wiki/File:Map-Hindustani_World.png" class="image"><img alt="Map-Hindustani World.png" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/Map-Hindustani_World.png/230px-Map-Hindustani_World.png" width="230" height="239" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/Map-Hindustani_World.png/345px-Map-Hindustani_World.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/69/Map-Hindustani_World.png 2x" data-file-width="347" data-file-height="361" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Bengali_language" title="Bengali language">Bengali</a></td>\n<td>242&#160;M</td>\n<td>261&#160;M<sup id="cite_ref-41" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-41">[41]</a></sup></td>\n<td><small>Official language in: <a href="/wiki/Bangladesh" title="Bangladesh">Bangladesh</a> and in the Indian states of <a href="/wiki/West_Bengal" title="West Bengal">West Bengal</a>, <a href="/wiki/Tripura" title="Tripura">Tripura</a> and <a href="/wiki/Assam" title="Assam">Assam</a></small></td>\n<td><a href="/wiki/File:Bengali-world.png" class="image"><img alt="Bengali-world.png" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a7/Bengali-world.png/230px-Bengali-world.png" width="230" height="117" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a7/Bengali-world.png/345px-Bengali-world.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a7/Bengali-world.png/460px-Bengali-world.png 2x" data-file-width="2753" data-file-height="1400" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Malay_language" title="Malay language">Malay</a> and <a href="/wiki/Indonesian_language" title="Indonesian language">Indonesian</a></td>\n<td>39&#160;M</td>\n<td>218&#160;M<sup id="cite_ref-42" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-42">[42]</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-43" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-43">[43]</a></sup></td>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Nusantara" title="Nusantara">Nusantara</a> (<a hr